description:
In the inaugural Mariah POP Dive, Danny dives into the first 5 years of Mariah Carey's illustrious career with musician/lamb/gem Matt Palmer. They discuss the first 5 albums of Mariah's career- everything from her self-titled debut album through Daydream.


*To support this podcast & for bonus episodes, head over to Patreon.com/EverythingIconic.
